    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine. This example maintains its sequential twin-turbocharger setup, delivering linear power through the rev range with a crisp transition at 4,500 RPM. The chassis remains rigid, benefiting from the factory double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential that ensures exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. Recent service includes a cooling system overhaul and apex seal compression check, confirming strong internal health. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and underpinnings are dialed for the driving enthusiast. A pure, analog experience with a balanced front-midship layout.",
