    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a meticulously maintained luxury SUV that offers a refined driving experience. The exterior features a deep Eminent White Pearl finish that still holds a showroom-like luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood from regular highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the Parchment leather upholstery is soft and free of cracks, and the genuine wood trim remains vibrant. All onboard technology, including the intuitive navigation system and the premium Mark Levinson sound system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine runs quietly and delivers smooth, consistent power through the 8-speed automatic transmission. It has a complete service history, with a recent brake service and a fresh set of tires installed just 3,000 miles ago. This is a non-smoker vehicle that has been garage-kept, ensuring it remains in excellent shape for its next owner.",
